SELECT
  i_item_id,
  AVG(ss_quantity) AS agg1,
  AVG(ss_list_price) AS agg2,
  AVG(ss_coupon_amt) AS agg3,
  AVG(ss_sales_price) AS agg4
FROM (
  SELECT
    *
  FROM store_sales
) AS ss, (
  SELECT
    *
  FROM customer_demographics
  WHERE
    cd_gender = 'F' AND cd_marital_status = 'W' AND cd_education_status = 'College'
) AS cd, (
  SELECT
    *
  FROM date_dim
  WHERE
    d_year = 2001
) AS d, (
  SELECT
    *
  FROM item
) AS i, (
  SELECT
    *
  FROM promotion
  WHERE
    p_channel_email = 'N' OR p_channel_event = 'N'
) AS p
WHERE
  ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
  AND ss_item_sk = i_item_sk
  AND ss_cdemo_sk = cd_demo_sk
  AND ss_promo_sk = p_promo_sk
GROUP BY
  i_item_id
ORDER BY
  i_item_id
LIMIT 100

WITH filtered_dates AS (
  SELECT
    d_date_sk
  FROM date_dim
  WHERE
    d_year = 2001
)
SELECT
  i_item_id,
  AVG(ss_quantity) AS agg1,
  AVG(ss_list_price) AS agg2,
  AVG(ss_coupon_amt) AS agg3,
  AVG(ss_sales_price) AS agg4
FROM store_sales, customer_demographics, filtered_dates, item, promotion

  ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk

  )

SELECT
  i.i_item_id,
  c.agg1_filter1 AS agg1,
  c.agg2_filter1 AS agg2,
  c.agg3_filter1 AS agg3,
  c.agg4_filter1 AS agg4
FROM item AS i
JOIN combined_scan AS c
  ON i.i_item_sk = c.ss_item_sk
WHERE
  NOT c.agg1_filter1 IS NULL /* Equivalent to HAVING */
ORDER BY

LIMIT 100
